### Content Structure
1. **Article Format**
   - Title: 60-70 characters
   - Meta description: 150-160 characters
   - Featured image: 1200x630px
   - Body: Markdown/Rich text
   - Categories and tags

2. **Typography**
   - Body text: 18-21px
   - Line height: 1.6
   - Paragraph spacing: 1.5em
   - Headers: modular scale 1.2

3. **Layout Principles**
   - Content width: 680px-720px
   - Sidebar width: 300px-320px
   - Grid system: 12 columns
   - Reading progress indicator

## ğŸ“Š Performance Requirements

1. **Content Loading**
   - Lazy loading images
   - Infinite scroll/pagination
   - Content preloading
